IPTV server

The IPTV server we got is a combination of a Content Manager and Server.
It is basically a PC with HD and the Content Manager software.

Login: Administrator
Password: (none)

The PC monitor, keyboard and mouse ports are located in the rear of the box.
The front has ports for the content manager.

The console port of the IPTV server does not work.

Instead, we use the Web page configuration throught Ethernet connection.

Connect Laptop Ethernet port with the IPTV Ethernet 0 port.
Configurate the Laptop Ethernet port with appropriate IP address
and subnet mask.
Go to web page (IP address).
Login: admin
Password: admin


NOTE: Make sure the unused Ethernet interface is disabled to ensure the
      content is streamed out from the correct interface!!

Don't serve more than 1 channel at a time!
I could not make live vide work if there is another schedule program going on!


